title: Guerrilla Warfare Training.wmv
description:
Tired of keyboard commandos?

I took a road trip with a few of our own and rendezvoused with the Hutaree (one of the many Michigan militia battalions). They allowed me to sport their uniform and we compiled this promotional video. Enjoy!

"In the beginning of change, the patriot is a scarce man, and brave, and hated and scorned. When his cause succeeds, the timid join him, for it then costs nothing to be a patriot."
- Mark Twain
